text: Gunnar Pedersen (born 23 September 1924) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aarhus
